Hello, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. My name is Emily. How can I assist you today?

Hi Emily, I'm having an issue with my billing and need some help.

Of course, I'd be happy to help with that. May I have your name please?

Sure, my name is Alex Johnson.

Thank you, Alex. Can you please provide me with your account number? You can find it on the top right corner of your billing statement.

Yes, it's two zero three five zero one.

Great, thank you. For verification purposes, could you also provide me with the last four digits of your phone number?

Certainly, the last four digits are five six seven eight.

I appreciate your help, Alex. Let me pull up your billing information... I have it here. Is there a specific charge you are concerned about?

Yes, there seems to be an extra charge this month under lane maintenance, and I’m not sure why.

Let me check into that extra charge for you... It looks like there was a maintenance fee which was mistakenly applied to your account. I'll remove that charge right away.

Thank you so much for sorting this out!

You're welcome, Alex. Thank you for your patience. If there's anything else you need help with, feel free to call us back. Have a great day!
